Mirror the COR-015 fraction-of-stored-days approach in the approve gate: instead of recomputing via `splitLeaveByYear` (which cannot recover `endHalfDay`), use the stored `leave.days` as the total and derive year fractions from `splitLeaveByYear` proportions:
